data.description: Check out this gorgeous 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home. This home features an open floor plan which includes two living areas, one on each level perfect for entertaining.  The formal dining room is adjacent to the kitchen. A huge master suite is located on the first floor, including a master bath. This home is minutes away from shopping, popular dining, and easy access to US67 and I20.
